  "title": "Part-time English Teacher (Primary)",
  "description": "<p>Since year 2000, Lynn Learning Hub has successfully taught thousands of students in English, Mathematics, Science, Chinese and Economics. </p><p><br /></p><p>We offer challenging career opportunities to the right individuals. As the Group expands further, we are seeking qualified individuals with their expertise, integrity and dedication to join our winning team. Join us today!</p><p><br /></p><p>Position 1:</p><p>Job Scope</p><ul><li>To conduct group tuition for English language</li><li>To follow the teaching guide provided</li><li>To update the students' attendance daily and progress report monthly</li><li>Provide feedback to parents</li></ul><p>Job Requirements</p><ul><li>He / She must possess a diploma or degree </li><li>A good grade in English</li><li>Passion for teaching and nurturing young minds</li><li>Good classroom management; able to handle up to 12 students</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Able to work in the West</li></ul><p>Position 2:</p><p>Job Scope</p><ul><li>To conduct group tuition for English Reading</li><li>To follow the teaching guide provided</li><li>To update the students' attendance daily and progress report monthly</li><li>Provide feedback to parents</li></ul><p>Job Requirements</p><ul><li>Prior teaching experience in Phonics is required</li><li>Passion for teaching and nurturing young minds</li><li>Good classroom management; able to handle up to 12 students</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Able to work in the West</li></ul><p>Schedule</p><ul><li>Tuesday evenings </li></ul><p>If you're ready to embark on a fulfilling journey in education, we want to hear from you! Please submit your resume and a cover letter detailing your teaching philosophy and relevant experience.</p>",
